  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Element Construction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    All skills can be freely assigned to any soldier unit. Equip and mix items freely without restrictions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    Progression System</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Units, equipment, and skills can all be upgraded to higher tiers, continuously empowering your army.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    Infinite Stages</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Test your strategies with limitless combinations of units, skills, and gear. There are no constraints—let your imagination run wild.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    Roguelike Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    After each stage, choose from a variety of random elemental rewards. Every tower climb promises a fresh and unique experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    Genetic Algorithm AI Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    In infinite mode, the AI uses a genetic algorithm to analyze and adapt to your strategies over time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >    Ancient Han & Three Kingdoms Units</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    The game is set during the late Han dynasty and the Three Kingdoms era. Command historically inspired units to crush your enemies!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a solo-developed, infinite-stage AI Auto Chess game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a genetic algorithm, allowing AI opponents to grow smarter over time by learning from battles against the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/9087b6bf9ed9c8cd9d373e6a860ef95f.poster.avif?t=1746594665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/9087b6bf9ed9c8cd9d373e6a860ef95f.webm?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/9087b6bf9ed9c8cd9d373e6a860ef95f.mp4?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy real-time combat, free element combinations, and roguelike progression. Build a unique legion, discover powerful synergies between elements, and explore the strategic depth of elemental combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/f1990a3db51fc47783387cc7428828a8.poster.avif?t=1746594665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/f1990a3db51fc47783387cc7428828a8.webm?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/f1990a3db51fc47783387cc7428828a8.mp4?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a solo-developed, infinite-stage AI Auto Chess game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a genetic algorithm, allowing AI opponents to grow smarter over time by learning from battles against the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/9087b6bf9ed9c8cd9d373e6a860ef95f.poster.avif?t=1746594665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/9087b6bf9ed9c8cd9d373e6a860ef95f.webm?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/9087b6bf9ed9c8cd9d373e6a860ef95f.mp4?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy real-time combat, free element combinations, and roguelike progression. Build a unique legion, discover powerful synergies between elements, and explore the strategic depth of elemental combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/f1990a3db51fc47783387cc7428828a8.poster.avif?t=1746594665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/f1990a3db51fc47783387cc7428828a8.webm?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3383020/extras/f1990a3db51fc47783387cc7428828a8.mp4?t=1746594665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
